title: "Canadian water-policy trilogy: agricultural water pollution, farmland consolidation risk, and cost–benefit incidence"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-07-21"
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Crandlemire
    given-names: John
